<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>HYMN TO THE GLORIOUS CROSS</B></FONT></H2>
<H3><PRE>

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   E                 G#            C#m
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. The glorious cross of the risen Lord
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          F#m           G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   is the tree of my salvation;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       E               G#              C#m
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   I feed myself on it, in it I take delight,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           F#m           B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in its roots I grow up,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                     E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in its branches I lie down.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   G#               A
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. Its dew makes me glad,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   its breeze fecundates me,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           F#m                 G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in its shadow I have put my tent
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       A
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   In hunger nourishment, in thirst the fountain,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in nakedness clothing.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   F#m                  G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Hard path, my narrow way,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   F#m
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Jacob's ladder, bed of love
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   where the Lord has espoused us.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   E                 G#            C#m
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. The glorious cross of the risen Lord
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">          F#m           G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   is the tree of my salvation;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       E               G#              C#m
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   I feed myself on it, in it I take delight,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           F#m           B7
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in its roots I grow up,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                     E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in its branches I lie down.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   G#          A
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. In fear defense,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in stumbling support,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       A
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in victory crown
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                               G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in the struggle you are the reward.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   F#m             G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Tree of eternal life,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   F#m               G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   pillar of the universe,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   A
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   frame of the earth, your top reaches heaven,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and in your open arms
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                      G#
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   shines the love of God.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">   E                 G#            C#m
